{"tid":636892,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[獨家消息] 退而不休 雲格想轉教國家隊或做總監","createTime":"2018-04-21T10:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T01:03:22.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11fe8e29e9e88c3c11cd5d3389cacf685677b62f","tid":636892,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴領隊雲格宣佈離隊的決定令人意外，<span style=\"color: red;\">但Goal得到消息</span>，「教授」離開不等如退休，他將即時回歸球壇轉任國家隊教頭或球會體育總監等職位。<br />\n<br />\n雲格今次決定事出突然，事實上他一直沒有向任何人透露有關想法，只在周五練習前突然向教練團宣佈決定，而他不會像費格遜般，在兵工廠下任領隊給予任何要求或意見。<br />\n<br />\n雲格希望這個決定可令球隊在今季餘下時間團結一致，在歐霸盃爭取冠軍，從而取得下屆歐聯入場券。而他離隊後亦不會休息太久，消息指他希望轉任國家隊領隊或球會體育總監等職務。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=fchuQbFKY0nEdUBkMLtXEtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=095074f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"b130cfa201dd19c10ca9ea3b647419d1853b50ce","tid":636892,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e53eda8c8c8935ea312d825f5a66d9a73501a8a","tid":636892,"uid":312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"港隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950894eab572c9f40e91a02e398a0c22ccf9b90e","tid":636892,"uid":34517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"邊個國家隊先 <br />\n法國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598660198e71211d5898eb8201cff68f9bf81574","tid":636892,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9b68f6c0b2ed305b9459504c7fe13839af61d2c","tid":636892,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2